  "description": "A privacy-first PDF processing engine that deconstructs documents into their core elements—text, images, and tables—and reconstructs them into pristine, structured Markdown. Self-hosted React + FastAPI stack with local AI vision models via LiteLLM/Ollama. Your data never leaves your machine.",
